    "description": "想从新角度体验益智游戏吗？<br><br>     ……转动轮盘……<br><br>在《Cylinder》中赚取高分！<br><br>《Cylinder》这款光芒闪耀的益智游戏节奏明快，颜色鲜亮且吸引力十足。你可以按照自己的方式来畅玩。小心！不要让你的Cylinder（圆柱体）失控，还可以与他人竞争！你能打出漂亮的连击吗？你敢挑战益智难题吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357410/extras/14cbcfa94173ec27f3080bc497ffd007.poster.avif?t=1726242606\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357410/extras/14cbcfa94173ec27f3080bc497ffd007.webm?t=1726242606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357410/extras/14cbcfa94173ec27f3080bc497ffd007.mp4?t=1726242606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>在多种游戏模式中旋转获胜！</u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你在单人游戏中能前进多远？你能达到排行榜的首位吗？<br></li><li>在多人游戏中快速行动并策动特殊攻击！<br></li><li>解谜模式：挑战超过200个难题<br></li><li>在编辑器中制作自己的谜题</li></ul><br><u>自定义体验《Cylinder》的方式</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357410/extras/df807303a0cacb013e493b2dff0b5261.poster.avif?t=1726242606\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357410/extras/df807303a0cacb013e493b2dff0b5261.webm?t=1726242606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357410/extras/df807303a0cacb013e493b2dff0b5261.mp4?t=1726242606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><u>多人游戏体验功能齐全</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357410/extras/e3c33df7f3dca816b90b8da4d4da6610.poster.avif?t=1726242606\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store